The example shows the interactive Qt application that combines the the example:
http://artis.imag.fr/Members/Gilles.Debunne/QGLViewer/examples/animation.html 
and the ROOT TCanvas with 2D histogram to represent the particles "speed vs position".


   1. To create the your platform makefile:
      "rm -rf .rootrc"  -- Unix ONLY
      "qmake"
      Attention. One may require to change the  HelloGLViewer.pro
      ---------  to edit the QGLViewer  installation directory
      
   2. To build the application type:
      Unix:
         "make"
      Windows ( no Cygwin!!! ):
         "nmake"    
      
      
   3. To start the example
      " HelloGLViewer"
      
  
